      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### What to compare\n- SWAG `auth request unexpected status`\n- oauth2-proxy `/oauth2/auth` return code\n- oauth2-proxy `/oauth2/start?...` redirect behavior\n- whether `/oauth2/auth` returns **401** and not **400**\n\n### Core queries\n```logql\n{stack=\"zone-proxy\", service=\"swag\"} |= \"auth request unexpected status\"\n```\n\n```logql\n{stack=\"zone-proxy\", service=\"oauth2-proxy\"} |= \"/oauth2/auth\"\n```\n\n```logql\n{stack=\"zone-proxy\", service=\"oauth2-proxy\"} |= \"/oauth2/start\"\n```\n"
      }
    }
